## UI Direction

### Overall style

| Area            | Current issue    | Suggested change                                          |
| --------------- | ---------------- | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| Summary ribbons | Too loud         | Use muted background + small status dot                   |
| Tables          | Too dominant     | Convert top view into compact cards                       |
| Colors          | High saturation  | Use soft green/amber/red/grey                             |
| Layout          | Spreadsheet-like | Dashboard sections: Summary → Actions → Details           |
| Data density    | Too much visible | Progressive disclosure: show details only on click/expand |

